About Us - Hutaib Electricals

We are Pune based manufacturers, supplier, and exporter of outstanding variety of

cable trays

, raceways draw boxes & industrial fabrications. The company has expertise in manufacturing products like

perforated cable trays

,

ladder type cable trays,

trunking cable trays / raceways, basket trays / wire mesh cable trays, junction boxes, raceways boxes and their accessories such as bends, elbows, tees, cross, reducers, and many more. Hutaib Electricals is located at Burhani Industrial Area in Pune which is a renowned industrial area.

Infrastructure

We encompass a state-of-art infrastructure which includes modern manufacturing unit, quality control unit and packing unit with all other accessories to achieve maximum quality and prompt delivery. Our location at Pune is an ideal place that is connected by all means to various parts of the country. All necessary support & services for manufacturing, supplying, and exporting products are available within close vicinity thereby enabling us to accomplish our targets within specified time frame and provide the

best quality cable trays and accessories

economically and promptly to clients.

Quality Policy

Our company has gained reputation in market for its matchless

trunking cable trays

/ raceways, basket tray, and industry fabrications which are available in many designs and specification as per customers' demands. The company has recruited a team of qualified and experienced technocrats who have acquired expertise in this art. In order to offer quality at best prices, we have maintained a well-equipped infrastructure enabling our manpower to fabricate products in bulk. Our quality assurance team works untiringly to maintain international standards in our product range We have carved a distinct niche in the market.
